8.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Tiktok-logo-on-screen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Tiktok-logo-on-screen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Tiktok-logo-on-screen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一位受欢迎的 TikToker 因未经许可使用受版权保护的样本而被索尼音乐起诉，现在必须支付超过 80 万美元的赔偿金。</p><p>早在 2022 年，音乐产业巨头就向亚利桑那州艺术家 Trefuego（真名 Dantreal Daevon Clark-Rainbolt）对其歌曲“90mh”发出了严格的版权删除通知。索尼随后对 Trefurego 提起诉讼，称其“公然且蓄意侵犯”日本作曲家日向俊文 (Hinata) 1986 年的歌曲《Reflections》。</p><p>根据诉讼称，“Trefuego……只是窃取了 Hinata 的音乐作品和录音，在未经询问和许可的情况下使用它们，所有这些都公然违反了美国版权法。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C15lq3euqAT/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 